Package: llm.api
Title: Minimal LLM Chat Interface
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Troy", "Hernandez", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "troy@cornball.ai",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0005-4248-604X")),
    person("ellmer team", role = "cph",
           comment = "API design derived from ellmer"))
Description: A minimal-dependency client for Large Language Model APIs.
    Supports OpenAI, Anthropic Claude, Moonshot Kimi, Ollama, and other
    OpenAI-compatible endpoints, plus local inference via 'localLLM'.
    Includes an agent loop with tool use and a Model Context Protocol
    client. API design derived from 'ellmer', reimplemented with only
    base R, 'curl', and 'jsonlite'.
